  # 1. Define the nested specifications
  baseline_rhs <- "origin_region + years_in_us + age_centered"
  full_rhs     <- "origin_region + years_in_us + age_centered + educ_cat + currently_married + log_income"
2. Update h3-interaction
You will need to update the formula string here as well, and also update the filtering logic lower down in the chunk so it properly searches for years_in_us instead of yiu_clean when printing the table.

Replace the int_rhs definition near the top of the chunk:

